<item>
            <title>[LU-19953] Avoid exclusive VFS locking for parallel unlinks in -&gt;unlink()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19953</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/53169&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/53169&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17295&quot; title=&quot;avoiding VFS exclusive locking on shared parent directory in -&amp;gt;atomic_open()&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17295&quot;&gt;LU-17295&lt;/a&gt; avoids the VFS lock and enables parallel creates. It demonstrated about a 20&#215; performance boost for file creation in a single shared directory.&lt;br/&gt;
It would be nice to have the same improvement for unlink operations in a shared directory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
